        "title": "4. `fetchers.py` — the largest untested surface",
        "content": "\nThis file has ~20 `parse_*` pure functions (each with defensive/positional field access worth locking down) and ~15 `fetch_*` async functions that need `httpx.MockTransport`. Given the size, prioritize:\n\n**A. Pure parsers — high value, cheap to write.** Pattern to replicate across every `parse_*`:\n\n```python\n",
